A = [1, 2]
B = [2, 4]

D = [1, 0]
inputs = pd.DataFrame({'A': A, 'B': B, 'C': C})

    inputs.iloc[:, ([1, 2])], outputs))]
expected = {(0): 1, (2): 3}
assert expected == _singlethread_iteration(selection_iterator, scoring_fn)
